      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied this car, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but at a much better price, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
