    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically impeccable E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six. This unit features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with a recent Shim-and-Bucket adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding a 3.62 final drive ratio through a healthy M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points\u2014addressing the platform's primary structural concern\u2014while the suspension bushings and dampers remain in factory-new condition. The Laguna Seca Blue finish is flawless, retaining its deep luster with no evidence of road rash or clear coat failure. This is a turn-key, collector-grade machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
